# Project
# regenerable: HF stream cache + Parquet output
data/

# Paid artifacts — committed so `make eval`/`make bench`/`make charts` reproduce
# every README number offline with zero Cohere quota (public web-text embeddings
# + our own Command A label scores; nothing secret). Runtime WAL/shm files stay
# ignored via the broad rule below.
.cache/*
!.cache/label_cache.json
!.cache/embeddings/
.cache/embeddings/*
!.cache/embeddings/cache.db

# eval outputs: commit the small JSON reports + the pre-embedded bench input so
# `make charts`/`make bench` run on a fresh clone; ignore everything else.
eval/results/*
!eval/results/.gitkeep
!eval/results/eval_report.json
!eval/results/plot_data.json
!eval/results/bench_input.parquet

# docs: internal working docs (PRD/TDD) — kept local
# Public artifacts (demo.gif, architecture.md) live in assets/.
docs/

# session-transfer note 
handoff.md

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
